president bush says america is making progress 
in the war against drugs but cops on the nations streets say its 
still pretty bad out there and not getting any better 
its getting worse by leaps and bounds said police lt josh 
landers of yonkers ny one of more than two dozen law 
enforcement officials nationwide surveyed by the associated press 
its crazy 
were dying out here said narcotics detective margaret 
