although all those accepted scored passing grades some of the 
blacks accepted scored lower than some of the rejected whites the 
200 people who passed the first hurdle are competing for only 40 
slots in the police academy class that begins nov 1 
the citys civil service commission is operating under a court 
decree that requires 45 percent of three upcoming police academy 
