middleage couple perspiring from the exhausting uphill hike to the 
school and the artzi family their little girl sucking furiously 
at her pacifier as the instructor described symptoms of gas 
poisoning trembling bodily secretions inflamed eyes 
this is the injection orange up green down barked the 
toughlooking instructor in olivegreen uniform 
how do you remember easy orange the sun up green the 
grass down 
the army instructors also handed out leaflets in hebrew arabic 
russian and english hebrew and russian placards decorated the 
walls 
there was no hint of panic the schools were empty for the 
jewish festival of sukkot so no classes were disrupted yoqneam 
snoozed away the hot afternoon hours 
men played backgammon in a coffee shop a car driven by hassidic 
jews passed by with music blaring from loudspeakers towing a 
mobile sukkah the traditional hut in which the observant spend the 
eightday holiday 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

